    Class and Description
    AdditionalExp
    This class is dedicated to the methods of how bonus experience is given when a player is skilling, fighting, etc..
    Perks 
    SkillCapeBonuses
    When the player is training the specific skill from #SkillCapeBonuses(int, int) and is wearing the correct SkillCapeBonuses.capes they will receive addition SkillCapeBonuses.exp upon every skill execution.
    SkillIndex
    The @enum SkillIndex.SkillIndex(int, double) is used for getting the SkillIndex.getSkillId() and SkillIndex.expRatio when adding skill exp when training a specific skill, or used however else.
